CODEOWNERS File for HR System (Payroll Subsystem Integration)

This file defines who owns specific parts of the codebase.

GitHub automatically requests reviews from these owners when a Pull Request touches these files.

-------------------------------------------------------------------

1. BACKEND MODULE OWNERSHIP (NestJS)

-------------------------------------------------------------------

1.1 Payroll Configuration & Policy Subsystem

Files defining core policies, pay grades, tax rules, and insurance.

Owner: Moussa

/backend/src/payroll-configuration/ @moussa101

1.2 Payroll Processing & Execution Subsystem

Files handling salary calculation, payroll runs, penalties, and payslip generation.

Owner: Omar

/backend/src/payroll-execution/ @omarbelo23

1.3 Payroll Tracking, Transparency & Self-Service Subsystem

Files handling employee disputes, claims, and tracking history.

Owner: Marwan

/backend/src/payroll-tracking/ @MarwanHulk

